Class InstrumentedExtractorDecorator<S,D>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.instrumented.extractor.InstrumentedExtractorBase<S,D>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Instrumentable, Extractor<S,D>, Decorator, FinalState, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class InstrumentedExtractorDecorator<S,D>
extends InstrumentedExtractorBase<S,D>
implements Decorator
    Decorator that automatically instruments Extractor. Handles already instrumented InstrumentedExtractor appropriately to avoid double metric reporting.
